* Iron Raptor bared her teeth up at Nightstrike, suddenly realizing that 
Prowl had opened his mind up to her just then.
< Excellent!>
But soon her mind focused on Nightstrike again, snarling at what he said 
about the Maximals.*

" YOUR RACE IS IN ITS PLACE, NIGHTSTRIKE!"

* Suddenly, without warning she transformed into her SBM, the large black 
form of the Nostelgia ( Alien ) rising an incredable 15 ft. Her shadow 
decended upon Nightstrike.*

" AT THE BOTTOM OF THE FOOD CHAIN!"

* Her voice boomed before a wave of acid sprayed towards Nightstrike.
Her mind directed Prowl's free thoughts to mingle with hers and join in the 
same form of attack.*
